'''迈克·马卡里'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael "Mike" Macari'''}}；{{bd|1973年|2月4日}}）是[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]的前职业足球运动员，曾为一名[[前锋_(足球)|前锋]]。

==职业生涯==
马卡里进入[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联足球俱乐部]]标志他的职业生涯开始，在进入[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|斯托克城足球俱乐部]]之前，于1996至1997年间在足球联合会出场30次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neilbrown.newcastlefans.com/stoke/stoke.htm|title=STOKE CITY : 1946/47 - 2008/09|accessdate=15 December 2009|publisher=Post War English & Scottish Football League A - Z Player's Database|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212205156/http://www.neilbrown.newcastlefans.com/stoke/stoke.htm|archivedate=2009年12月12日}}</ref>。

==家庭==
马卡里的父亲娄马卡里和弟弟保罗·马卡里也是职业足球运动员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/football-he-wants-his-football-not-his-name-to-do-the-talking-1292836.html|title=Football: 'He wants his football not his name to do the talking'|accessdate=15 December 2009|date=8 November 1997|author=Olivia Blair|publisher=''The Independent''|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105102726/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/football-he-wants-his-football-not-his-name-to-do-the-talking-1292836.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一位兄弟在离开[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部]]后自杀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/331687.stm|title=Football manager's son found hanged|accessdate=15 December 2009|date=29 April 1999|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2009-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090521183203/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/331687.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

